<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">I wasn&apos;t really into books in elementary school cause i&apos;ve never been good at ELA so it was a pain just learning to read. My favorite book at the time<a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">I wasn't really into books in elementary school cause i've never been good at ELA so it was a pain just learning to read. My favorite book at the time was Cloudy With A Chance Of Meatballs (Was so happy when the movie came out) and it was 4th grade where my teacher read us the book.<br />I loved it so much that I read it twice and after that I got into books more though I really got into reading during the 7th grade.<br />Now I can't get enough XD<a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
