<div id="review_54593466" class="review nosyndicate" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/54593466" />
    <a title="Laura" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/1394928-laura"><img alt="Laura" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1405367803p2/1394928.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/54593466?book_show_action=true">May 01, 2009</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Laura" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Laura" href="/user/show/1394928-laura">Laura</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="really liked it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">really liked it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>



        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/1394928-laura?shelf=xx-2010-xx">xx-2010-xx</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/1394928-laura?shelf=2019">2019</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/1394928-laura?shelf=overdrive">overdrive</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer54593466" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer5981051666646657111">I&apos;ve now read this for the third time, every time as an adult. This is a book about the power of love and kindness. It is about how we are more alike than we are different. Important ideas to reinforce, and becoming more important by the day. <br/><br/>Highly recommended to kids of all ages and the audio performance is beautifully and sensitively performed. <br/><br/>&lt;&gt;&lt;&gt;&lt;&gt;<br/><br/><br/>I loved this book. There are so many great lessons for kids about doing the right thing, being brave, forgiving and having empathy for others. I</span>
  <span id="freeText5981051666646657111" style="display:none">I've now read this for the third time, every time as an adult. This is a book about the power of love and kindness. It is about how we are more alike than we are different. Important ideas to reinforce, and becoming more important by the day. <br /><br />Highly recommended to kids of all ages and the audio performance is beautifully and sensitively performed. <br /><br />&lt;&gt;&lt;&gt;&lt;&gt;<br /><br /><br />I loved this book. There are so many great lessons for kids about doing the right thing, being brave, forgiving and having empathy for others. It was very well-written. I also loved the author asides, as it brought an interesting flavor to the story and made it unique. The story itself was solid, but I liked the lessons and her delivery the best. I definitely want to read more by this author.<br /><br />*read this book again, and loved it, maybe even more than before. I'm reading another by her now too. What a nice, gentle read with some great messages for kids.</span>
  <a data-text-id="5981051666646657111" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
