        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2959437877" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer10843227210927243511">For all of us who can still be mesmerized by these magical words: &quot;Once upon a time...&quot; this story defies time and age. <br/><br/>Once again, I picked up a book because of its beautiful cover and although it is mainly intended for children, I found it riveting and magical. I actually feel that, had I read this at a younger age, I would have missed plenty of it&apos;s subtlety and lyrical prose. So, definitely a new favourite for me.</span>
  <span id="freeText10843227210927243511" style="display:none">For all of us who can still be mesmerized by these magical words: "Once upon a time..." this story defies time and age. <br /><br />Once again, I picked up a book because of its beautiful cover and although it is mainly intended for children, I found it riveting and magical. I actually feel that, had I read this at a younger age, I would have missed plenty of it's subtlety and lyrical prose. So, definitely a new favourite for me.</span>
